HTTP/1.1 201 Created
Content-Length: 0
Date: REGEX(.*)
Location: /ngsi-ld/v1/entities/urn:ngsi-ld:entity:E3

HTTP/1.1 201 Created
Content-Length: 0
Date: REGEX(.*)
Location: /ngsi-ld/v1/entities/urn:ngsi-ld:entity:E4



02. Remove entities E1 and E3 using DELETE /ngsi-ld/v1/entities?type=T1
=======================================================================
HTTP/1.1 204 No Content
Date: REGEX(.*)



03. Get all entities - see E2 and E4
====================================
